title: Democrat demands release of 'shocking' Trump-Saudi call from 2019 after Khashoggi's death
description: WASHINGTON (Reuters) -A Democratic lawmaker who served on Donald Trump's National Security Council in his first term urged the White House on Friday to release a transcript of Trump's 2019 call with Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman after journalist Jamal Khashoggi's killing.
